Revert "Initialize structs declared within templated imports."

This reverts commit 12baa706a2162acd5a555af922105a4061fbd0f8.
Enable static builds even if pkg-config is missing; support static linking of gsl library.
Initialize structs declared within templated imports.
Rename virtual function to v to avoid confusion.
Slight improvement: `new T` now seems to work.
Restore LDFLAGS; don't look for tirpc under MacOS.
Define correct preprocessor symbol if static library is unavailable.
Rename HAVE_RPC_RPC_H to HAVE_LIBTIRPC; add --enable-xdr[=yes] configuration option.
Support --enable-static again; allow static builds of libtirpc.
Address issue #421: reduce redundant latexmk runs.
Address issue #424: Add support for latexmk -c.
